---
title: Easy Oven-Baked Mumbai Beef Biryani with Flaked Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Prepare your tastebuds for a magical journey with this hearty beef biryani. The deep Mumbai spice blend infused into the
basmati rice is beautifully complemented by a cooling yoghurt and a scattering of flaked almonds. Loaded with these rich tastes
of India, the whole family will be transported to a world of flavour!
